==Russian==

===Suffix===
'''-ов''' (-ov, -off)

# [['s]], [[-son]], [[-s]] ''(possessive suffix)''.
#:*[[Иванов]] &mdash; ''[[John|John’s]], [[Jones]], [[Johnson]]''
#:*[[Петров]] &mdash; ''[[Peter|Peter’s]], [[Peters]], [[Peterson]]''
#:*[[Христов]] &mdash; ''[[Christ|Christ’s]]''
# [['s]], [[of]] ''([[genitive case|genitive]] plural ending for most masculine nouns)''.
#:*{{RUchar|[[журнал|журна́лов]]}} &mdash; ''[[magazine|of the magazines]]''
#:*{{RUchar|[[отец|отцо́в]]}} &mdash; ''[[father|fathers’]], [[dad|dads’]]''
#:*{{RUchar|[[стол|столо́в]]}} &mdash; ''[[table|of the tables]]''

